might've taken a flyer here and there.

67
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:10,320
Around all that action, sooner or
later you're gonna shake the baby.

68
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,250
Gambling problem, multiple ex-wives...

69
00:04:12,251 --> 00:04:14,151
Gee, I wonder where the money went.

70
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:17,510
Coulda been in deep to somebody.
Made sure he paid up.

71
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:18,680
Dug his own grave.

72
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:20,600
You know,for a guy who liked
to shoot the works,

73
00:04:20,601 --> 00:04:23,601
Sandoval's record's clean,
not even a parking ticket.

74
00:04:23,740 --> 00:04:25,740
Yeah, no official record.

75
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:28,330
Sonny "Mil Hombres" Sandoval.

76
00:04:28,331 --> 00:04:32,831
Mil Hombres...
"strength of a thousand men ?"

77
00:04:32,910 --> 00:04:36,110
He needed it,keep up with the
ladies he was pulling down.

78
00:04:36,230 --> 00:04:39,420
Sonny was a rock star :
women, money, cars.

79
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,030
He got mixed up in any trouble,

80
00:04:41,031 --> 00:04:43,931
PPD gave him a pass just like
Iverson and Barkley.

81
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:45,340
Come on !

82
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:46,680
Jockeys ?

83
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:48,650
Those knee knockers
get the ladies ?

84
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,390
Hmm, still a man on a horse.

85
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,320
Confident, athlete...

86
00:04:53,121 --> 00:04:54,521
Winning combo.

87
00:04:55,210 --> 00:04:57,390
I'm saying this town loves a winner.

88
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,620
Somebody shoot me.

89
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:02,280
I'll beat the bushes with the local
bookies and loan sharks.

90
